name: I Looked Down Upon A Lake Of Fire And Knew
description:
The foundation for this artwork was generated from AI that I trained with hundreds of my oil paintings, followed by my alterations and refinements using various digital tools. OIL + GAN + digital manipulation + collage + remash with my paintings “Market Temple” and “At The Crossing”.
David A. N. Cheifetz, 2021
4381 × 3834
